			We primarily use Amazon’s U.S. East data center, which is located in Northern Virginia. However, <a href="/plans-pricing/wordpress-vps-hosting/">VPS</a> or <a href="/plans-pricing/enterprise-wordpress-hosting/">Enterprise WordPress</a> customers may request to be placed in any of Amazon’s global data centers. So no matter where your customers are, you can be located close to them.
